snippet.title: Jordan Peterson Fan Channel
snippet.description:
Did you know that Dr. Peterson even send an encouraging tweet linking to this channel and shared some of the clips via his Twitter and Facebook? Thank you! https://twitter.com/jordanbpeterson/status/896947751476502528
Jordan Peterson Fan Channel is also an official affiliate for his “Self Authoring” program: http://bit.ly/SelfAuthoring

If you like these videos, you should consider watching one of JBPs psychology classes from start, e.g. Maps of Meaning. There is much more to it than can be conveyed in such short clips: https://www.youtube.com/user/JordanPetersonVideos

Still, I wouldn’t mind if you subscribed to this channel too. . ;) 

If you happen to like the style of some of my thumbnails, I'm also for hire. Please feel free to contact me via the email address below.

As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases.

Thanks!
